tooltipText:
Costs 40 Courage

Slams the ground, dealing $hit2$ to enemies around you, while applying $effect:Status_Tripped$ for 2 seconds to targets that were $effect:Status_Staggered.hide$ and consuming the $effect:Status_Staggered.hide$ effect.  

Targets already $effect:Status_Tripped.hide$ are launched and take 25% more damage.
name: Tank_GroundPound
